<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<section xml:id="global-make-up-policy" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title> Make-Up Policy</title>
  <introduction>
    <p>
        There will be <em>NO MAKE-UP ASSIGNMENTS</em> for missed assignments. 
        You must make arrangements with me beforehand if you think you will miss an in-class assignment. 
        You may be allowed to take an exam early only if you have a substantiated excuse approved by the 
        instructor <em>before the due date</em>. Leaving a phone message or sending an e-mail without 
        confirmation is not acceptable.
    </p>
  </introduction>
</section>